# Continuous Intelligence

The platform does not stop after the first detection.

BCSentinel continuously monitors the evolution of every identified formation, updating its intelligence as new evidence becomes available.

Institutions receive an evolving intelligence process rather than a static report.

---

# Commercial Model

BCSentinel follows a high-value institutional licensing strategy.

The platform is designed around annual enterprise licenses granted to a limited number of institutional clients.

Each license includes:

• Continuous platform access

• Institutional Intelligence Packages

• Ongoing monitoring of active formations

• Intelligence updates

• Platform improvements

The objective is to establish long-term strategic relationships with a small number of institutional organizations rather than maximizing customer volume.

---

# Product Philosophy

BCSentinel does not sell blockchain alerts.

BCSentinel delivers institutional intelligence.

Every conclusion is supported by observable evidence, empirical validation and complete traceability.

The objective is not simply to detect activity.

The objective is to help institutions understand how future digital economic systems are being formed.

